          <outline text="From Notes" _note="Electronics 

Traveling - plane - charging
- iPhone (2) (USB C - lightning)
- iPad (2) (USB C - C)
-     1 USB C Apple Watch charger 
-     Hyperjuice 245W USB-C Battery Pack

Bring with:
       Hyperjuice 4 port USB C desk charger
 Cables:
  6 - USB-C to USB-C (i-Pads, battery pack, multi-device charging stands)
              1 USB C to lightning AirPods Max
  1 - USB-C to Mac
              1 - USB C to A (camera battery)
 Charging:
  2 - charging stands (phone, watch, AirPods) 

For the car (car interface)
1 USB C - lightning
1 USB A - lightning
" />
